Description: Very nice looking and playing small body acoustic-electric with strat-style headstock with very little scratching or wear that's a blast to play. This is the very well made 2000's Korean made Malibu SCE with solid spruce top and solid mahogany back and not the current laminate China made model.Hate to let it go but I have to slim down some how... Crafted with Solid mahogany back, and mahogany sides, and sweet playing neck with rosewood fingerboard and uniquely designed rosewood bridge. Fishman electronics with onboard tuner let you readily play with the band. Multiple top binding and a parquetry rosette add to classy look and feel."
